

:mod:`cache` -- Cache Maintenance Functions
===========================================

.. module:: cache

This module contains functions to help maintain the caches.


H2K_cache_l2_cleaninv
---------------------

.. c:function:: void H2K_cache_l2_cleaninv()

Description
~~~~~~~~~~~

This function cleans and invalidates the L2 cache.

H2K_cache_d_cleaninv
--------------------

.. c:function:: void H2K_cache_d_cleaninv()

Description
~~~~~~~~~~~

This function cleans and invalidates the Data cache.

H2K_cache_d_clean
-----------------

.. c:function:: void H2K_cache_d_clean()

Description
~~~~~~~~~~~

This function cleans the Data cache.

H2K_cache_i_inv
---------------

.. c:function:: void H2K_cache_i_inv()

Description
~~~~~~~~~~~

This function invalidates the Instruction cache.


